Descriptions

bhop_kz_downtheravine
Original map by SoUlFaThEr
contains 2 courses: bkz_downtheravine and bhop_ravine
notes: the map starts at the bottom

kz_mars
Original map by SoUlFaThEr
contains 2 courses: kz_mars and kz_ezblock
notes for server owners: set shavit_misc_startonspawn 0 and shavit_misc_resettargetname 0

kz_mix_mystery
Original map by Charles
contains 10 courses/minigames: kz_mix_mystery, bhop_conveyor_belt, mg_spiral_gauntlet, bhop_mind_and_matter, kz_goose, mg_dance_it_up, mg_pinball, bhop_straight_bhop, bhop_u_turn_bhop and mg_tic_tac_toe

kz_underground
Original map by Chrizzy
contains 2 courses: kz_underground and kz_powerplant

kz_verona
Original map by SoUlFaThEr
contains 2 courses: kz_verona and bhop_down_the_stairs

kz_xtremeblock_winter
Original map by Chrizzy
contains 2 courses: kz_xtremeblock and kz_lookout_tower
